## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Restart the Django dev server.
- Run `verify_safealert.py` to confirm all API endpoints are unaffected.
- Launch a new browser session via the browser subagent to:
  1. Log in.
  2. Take screenshots of each tab (Index, Verifikasi, Daftar User, Alarm Console) and verify the spacing and contrast are flawless.
  3. Validate that the status change AJAX dropdown behaves responsively.
